text: The Baojun Yunduo known as the Baojun Cloud in English sources is a electric compact Hatchback made by SAIC-GM-Wuling under the Baojun brand since 2023. == History and Features == The Baojun Yunduo was developed under the codename EQ100 it was shown in May 2023 with pre-sales in China. starting in June it has the Baojun's new design language called "Interstellar Geometry" its avaliable in three colors called Cloud Sea White, Cloud Twilight Purple and Cloud Smoke Qing the car has a electric motor with 100 kW (134 hp) and a range of 360-460 km (224-280 mi). == Markets == The Baojun Yunduo is sold mainly in the Chinese market but its also sold in Indonesia (as the Wuling Cloud EV) and in India (as the MG Windsor EV). == Sales == The MG Windsor EV became the best-selling electric car in India just one month after it was launched, selling over 3,000 units each month.
